  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nWhen switching to 1-to-1 chats the focus on the input field is lost.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to a community chat and focus the input field.\r\n    ![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2212681/218707297-cba84170-6c45-439e-aa5c-d150e07b62d6.png)\r\n2. Go to any 1-to-1 chat and see the loss of focus on input field.\r\n    ![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2212681/218707456-9740ea58-ed53-46ee-8a3c-1384ea442d20.png)\r\n\r\nThis works both when switching via mouse or using Ctrl+K shortcut.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nI keep focus and can start typing right away.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nI can't start typing.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: `v0.10.0-rc.7-2c3893`\r\n- Operating System: `Linux`\r\n\r\n",
